content.p: The School of Economics integrates excellence and innovation in teaching with an international reputation for high-quality research. Our courses combine all the core analytical and quantitative techniques required by modern economics graduates. Undergraduate degree courses Postgraduate taught courses Postgraduate research degrees School of Economics staff are recognised nationally and internationally for their influential and cutting-edge research. Read about some of their recent publications in top-tier academic journals. Sir Clive Granger Building University of Nottingham University Park Nottingham, NG7 2RD
